a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/EXSLT/regexp\">Regular expressions (regexp)</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/EXSLT/set\">Sets (set)</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/EXSLT/str\">Strings (str)</a></li></ol>\n  </ol>\n  <ol>\n    <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/XPath/Functions\"><strong>Functions</strong></a></li>\n    <ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/boolean\">boolean</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/ceiling\">ceiling</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/choose\">choose</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/concat\">concat</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/contains\">contains</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/count\">count</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/current\">current</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/document\">document</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/element-available\">element-available</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/false\">false</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/floor\">floor</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/format-number\">format-number</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/function-available\">function-available</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/generate-id\">generate-id</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/id\">id</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/key\">key</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/lang\">lang</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/last\">last</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/local-name\">local-name</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/name\">name</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/namespace-uri\">namespace-uri</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/normalize-space\">normalize-space</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/not\">not</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/number\">number</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/position\">position</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/round\">round</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/starts-with\">starts-with</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/string\">string</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/string-length\">string-length</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/substring\">substring</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/substring-after\">substring-after</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/substring-before\">substring-before</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/sum\">sum</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/system-property\">system-property</a></li><li><em><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/translate\" aria-current=\"page\">translate</a></em></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/true\">true</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/unparsed-entity-url\">unparsed-entity-url</a></li></ol>\n  </ol>\n  <ol>\n    <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/XPath/Axes\"><strong>Axes</strong></a></li>\n  </ol>\n","sidebarMacro":"XsltSidebar","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>The <code>translate</code> function evaluates a string and a set of characters to translate and returns the translated string.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"brush: plain notranslate\">translate(string, abc, XYZ)\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"arguments","title":"Arguments","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"string\"><a href=\"#string\"><code>string</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>The string to evaluate.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"abc\"><a href=\"#abc\"><code>abc</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>The string of characters that will be replaced.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"xyz\"><a href=\"#xyz\"><code>XYZ</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>The string of characters used for replacement. The first character in <code>XYZ</code> will replace every occurrence of the first character in <code>abc</code> that appears in <code>string</code>.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"returns","title":"Returns","isH3":true,"content":"<p>The translated string.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"notes","title":"Notes","isH3":true,"content":"<p>XPath notes that the translate function is not a sufficient solution for case conversion in all languages. A future version of XPath may provide additional functions for case conversion.</p>\n<p>However, this is the closest we have at present to a function that can convert a string to uppercase or lowercase.</p>\n<p>Example</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><p class=\"example-header\"><span class=\"language-name\">xml</span></p><pre class=\"brush: xml notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token namespace\">xsl:</span>value-of</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">select</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>translate('The quick brown fox.', 'abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz', 'ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZ')<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>Output</p>\n<pre class=\"brush: plain notranslate\">THE QUICK BROWN FOX.\n</pre>\n<ul>\n  <li>If <code>abc</code> is longer than <code>XYZ</code>, then every occurrence of characters in <code>abc</code> that do not have a corresponding character in <code>XYZ</code> will be removed.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Example</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><p class=\"example-header\"><span class=\"language-name\">xml</span></p><pre class=\"brush: xml notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token namespace\">xsl:</span>value-of</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">select</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>translate('The quick brown fox.', 'brown', 'red')<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>Output</p>\n<pre class=\"brush: plain notranslate\">The quick red fdx.\n</pre>\n<ul>\n  <li>If <code>XYZ</code> contains more characters than <code>abc</code>, the extra characters are ignored.</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"defined","title":"Defined","isH3":true,"content":"<p><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/1999/REC-xpath-19991116/#function-translate\" class=\"external\" target=\"_blank\">XPath 1.0 4.2</a></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"gecko_support","title":"Gecko support","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Supported.</p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"The translate function evaluates a string and a set of characters to translate and returns the translated string.","popularity":0.0026,"modified":"2023-10-25T09:31:33.000Z","source":{"folder":"en-us/web/xpath/functions/translate","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/blob/main/files/en-us/web/xpath/functions/translate/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/commit/dd4d084ae96d26ea5a11fac778109fa547a8aa9c","filename":"index.md"},"short_title":"translate","parents":[{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web","title":"References"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/XPath","title":"XPath"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/XPath/Functions","title":"Functions"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/translate","title":"translate"}],"pageTitle":"translate - XPath | MDN","noIndexing":false}}